{{Orphan|date=December 2016}} {{Infobox dancer | name = Misty Lown | image = | alt = | caption = | full_name = | birth_name = | birth_date = <!-- {{birth date and age|yyyy|mm|dd}} or {{birth date|yyyy|mm|dd}} --> | birth_place = | death_date = <!-- {{death date and age|deathyear|mm|dd|birthyear|mm|dd}} --> | death_place = | height = | occupation = Studio owner and dancer | years_active = | current_group = | former_groups = | dances = | website = {{URL|http://www.mistylown.com}} }}
'''Misty Lown''' is an American [[dance]] teacher and studio owner. She is the founder of ''Misty's Dance Unlimited'' and the ''More Than Just Great Dancing'' dance studio affiliate program.<ref>Jen Jones Donatelli (April 8, 2010). "[http://www.dance-teacher.com/2010/04/act-locally/ Act Locally]". ''Dance Teacher Magazine''. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Misty's Dance Unlimited Owner Brings Experiences with Success to Other Dance Studios|url=http://www.wxow.com/story/26741398/2014/10/08/mistys-dance-unlimited-owner-brings-experiences-with-success-to-other-dance-studios|accessdate=11 December 2014|publisher=WXOW|date=October 8, 2014}}</ref>
== Companies == She founded Misty's Dance Unlimited in 1998 in [[Onalaska, Wisconsin]].<ref>Jessie Foss (August/September 2011). "[http://www.crwmagazine.com/pdf/archive/crw-aug-sept2011.pdf The classroom is her stage]". ''CRW Magazine''. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref> Misty's Dance Unlimited teaches ballet, tap, jazz, hip hop, and beginner's classes. The studio integrates classes on community building and service into the dance curriculum.<ref>Staff (October 9, 2014). "[http://www.kwwl.com/story/26741398/2014/10/08/mistys-dance-unlimited-owner-brings-experiences-with-success-to-other-dance-studios Misty's Dance Unlimited Owner Brings Experiences with Success to Other Dance Studios]". [[KWWL (TV)|KWWL 7]]. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref> Lown is also the owner of More Than Just Great Dancing, an international affiliation program that establishes standards for dance programs and management.<ref>Staff (March 11, 2014). "[http://www.buffalonews.com/business/on-the-record/on-the-record-march-11-2014-20140310 On the Record / March 11, 2014]". [[The Buffalo News]]. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref><ref>Staff (April 5, 2013). "[http://www.southsidebusiness.com/southside/index.php/813-fountain-arts-center-joins-more-than-just-great-dancing-international Fountain Arts Center joins More Than Just Great Dancing International]". ''South Side Business''. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref> The program included 25 dance studios as of 2013.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Geyer|first1=Allison|title=Misty's Dance Unlimited: More than just great business|url=http://lacrossetribune.com/business/local/business-report/misty-s-dance-unlimited-more-than-just-great-business/article_6c9497ce-237d-11e2-9bde-001a4bcf887a.html|accessdate=11 December 2014|publisher=''[[La Crosse Tribune]]''|date=November 4, 2012}}</ref><ref name=":0">Allison Geyer (October 11, 2013). "[http://lacrossetribune.com/news/local/misty-s-dance-unlimited-earns-international-recognition/article_f70debc8-3270-11e3-b92c-0019bb2963f4.html Misty’s Dance Unlimited earns international recognition]". ''La Crosse Tribune''. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref> That year Lown and Misty's Dance Unlimited won Evoloshen's "Most Amazing Companies" award.<ref name=":0" />
She married her high school boyfriend and has five children.<ref>Jennifer Livingston (December 24, 2013). "[http://www.news8000.com/lifestyle/in-search-of/in-search-ofthe-inspiring-misty-lown/22753102 In Search Of...the inspiring Misty Lown]". [[WKBT-DT|News8000]]. Accessed November 21, 2014.</ref>
